         MACRO                                                                  
.* added by noid 06/01/87                                                       
.* macro returns location and length of seg buffer.                             
&L       TMSG                                                                   
&L       LABEL ,                                                                
         L     R1,CPSEGLOC                                                      
         LH    R0,CPSEGLEN                                                      
         MEND                                                                   
